{"tid":652742,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"關SIR: 五毛喺幾個dimension都有spectrum","createTime":"2018-05-04T05:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T14:26:54.000Z","uid":294,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3f4847bb31e513881ea54bf87dadcde4ff7ca585","tid":652742,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:40:12.000Z","msg":"1新舊/備用ac-<br />\n新/備用ac五毛, 應付大事, 方便同常規五毛扯貓尾。<br />\n常規五毛: e.g. dewi, JR, 岩瀨健三, Overbet<br />\n新ac: e.g. 佐維, 唔支持港獨<br />\n備用ac(潛水一排又上水/冇事就去其他台, 尤其體育台打躉): <br />\ne.g. 十卜ching, 美國佬<br />\n<br />\n2聲稱唔同政治取向-拉一派打一派<br />\n扮親泛民打壓本土: e.g. 未來撚啊廢, JR, 群龍共舞, D wade<br />\n擺明親中(而家比較少見, 因為唔work): e.g. 物產豐隆, 優美開始<br />\n<br />\n3明暗顯隱-<br />\n有啲懶中立扮正常但關鍵時刻現形嘅五毛: <br />\ne.g. D wade, 群龍共舞, 賈雨村<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有啲back up嘅隱性五毛。只會群埋其他五毛一齊抽水, 唔會表態親中反本</span><br />\ne.g. 夜子+, 水樹奈奈, 蓋世寶吊老母<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有啲比較低調, 偶然出現唔會反駁你</span><br />\ne.g. 羅拔利雲度夫斯基, 戚繼光<br />\n<br />\n4行文風格-<br />\n有啲一兩<span style=\"color: red;\">抽水玩膠, 成日問鍵國未, 買軍火未</span><br />\ne.g. Overbet, 唔支持港獨<br />\n有啲出長文懶有論述，但會無端端jump to conclusion 反港獨<br />\ne.g. 物產豐隆, JR<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/651054/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/651054/page/1</a><br />\n基本上唔係支持關sir都係五毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e38a95a5367c1d7983375e34424de93508b67a8","tid":652742,"uid":43861,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真共產黨"},{"pid":"792a56df144d15bea3c9f4c3086a34d70bdff67c","tid":652742,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a065b2b6b66583024127dd7992b82031e1d076","tid":652742,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0cbb7349552188effe9be2bfacc841b06ff2d0","tid":652742,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n3明暗顯隱-<br />\n有啲懶中立扮正常但關鍵時刻現形嘅五毛: <br />\ne.g. D wade, 群龍共舞, 賈雨村<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有啲back up嘅隱性五毛。只會群埋其他五毛一齊抽水, 唔會表態親中反本</span><br />\ne.g. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">夜子+</span>, 水樹奈奈, 蓋世寶吊老母<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有啲比較低調, 偶然出現唔會反駁你</span><br />\ne.g. 羅拔利雲度夫斯基, 戚繼光<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓主五毛</span>"},{"pid":"03ee8689dd114efc859df4baf68bfd4ecf66cce9","tid":652742,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1c0cbb7349552188effe9be2bfacc841b06ff2d0","tid":652742,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n3明暗顯隱-<br />\n有啲懶中立扮正常但關鍵時刻現形嘅五毛: <br />\ne.g. D wade, 群龍共舞, 賈雨村<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有啲back up嘅隱性五毛。只會群埋其他五毛一齊抽水, 唔會表態親中反本</span><br />\ne.g. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">夜子+</span>, 水樹奈奈, 蓋世寶吊老母<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有啲比較低調, 偶然出現唔會反駁你</span><br />\ne.g. 羅拔利雲度夫斯基, 戚繼光<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-